Vendor
Excuse me, I'm looking for something...
Yes？
I'm looking for a valuable book. The contents are like this...
Ah, in that case, I have it.
Huh, really？ Um, would you be willing to give me that book？
Let me think...
Then instead... I'll give you this camera part. What do you think？
...Okay, that's fine.
Thank you！
(I got the "Camera Part".)
Abbot
Excuse me. I'm looking for something... Can listen to my request？
Yes？
It's some kind of Buddha statue...
Ah, in that case, I have it.
Really？ Can I have your Buddha statue？
Let me think...
Then instead... I'll give you this pocket watch. What do you think？
...Okay, that's fine.
Ah！ Thank you very much.
(I got a "Pocket Watch".)
I've been here many times...
...Huh, what is that？
Some kind of charm... It looks like it has some kind of power.
(I got a "Charm against evil".)
I just come to buy some juice...
Oh, now that's what I call a nice bonus.
(I got a "Figure in a plastic bottle".)
Let's see if there's anything interesting here...
Oh, a poster. And it's free to take one...
(I got a "Poster of a Popular Artist".)
I been to Dixie's as costumer a lot...
I got a discount coupon... Even though I work part- time here.
(I got a "Dixie's discount coupon")
I've been to this store quite a bit...
I got a discount coupon... I'll come back soon.
(I got a discount coupon for the Aisha's Dining.)
Let's see what's good here...
Headphones, huh... I'll try them on.
I like them！ Okay...
(I purchased some "High-end headphones".)
Let's see if there's anything unusual here...
...Ah, this！ Amazing. This game is rarely sold...
Okay, I'll take this chance and get it...
(I got a "Very Rare Game Software".)
I'll if there's something of use...
A keyboard, huh... This is nice.
(I've got a "Gadgeteer's Keyboard".)
I've been to this store quite a bit...
Oh, they sell toys for cats...
(I got a "Toy Catnip".)
Guitarist
You're here a lot. Do you play any instruments？
Me？ Well...
Actually, I'm looking for someone to give this guitar. Would you be interested in taking it？
What？ It's fine by me, if you're sure you want to get rid of it...
Yeah. You've been coming here a lot, so you must like musical instruments, right？ Then, it's in safe hands...
In that case... Thank you so much.
See you. Nice to meet you.
(Got an "Acoustic Guitar".)
I remember I had a treasure map of this place...
Let's give it a try and see what I can find.
Should be around here...
Oh, there it is！ This is...
(I got a "Buddha Statue".)
Clerk
Excuse me. I'm actually looking for something... Can I have a moment？
Yes？
I'm looking for a map like this...
Ah, in that case, I have it.
Oh, really？ I wonder if you could give me that map.
Let me think...
Instead... I'll give you this precious book. What do you say？
...Okay, that's fine.
Thank you very much.
(I got a "Precious Book".)
Angler
You're here a lot, Onii-san.
Me？ Well...
We met here by chance so, do you want this fishing rod？
What？ I'm okay with that, if you're sure about it...
It just doesn't suit me. You should give it a try though.
Then... Thank you.
See you.
(I got a "Fishing Rod".)
Oba-chan
Onii-san, onii-san.
Me？ Emm...
I feel bad you're always here... I know, I found something, do you want to take it？
What？ I'd feel bad to receive it, but if you're sure...
It's fine, don't worry. Consider it a "thank you gift". My brother never used to play with these toys anyway.
Then... Thank you very much.
Keep up the good work.
(I got a "Nostalgic Toy Set".)
Farm Staff
Um, you come here a lot.
Me？ Well...
Here, it's just jam but, you can have it if you want？
What？ I mean yeah, I can take it if you want...
Yes. Thank you for always coming. Here you go.
Then... Thank you so much.
Thank you very much for your continued support.
(I got a "Jam".)
I've been to this store quite a bit...
I got a discount coupon... I'll come back soon.
(I got a discount coupon for an Italian Restaurant.)
I'm wondering if there is anything of use here...
Oh, the latest model of my racket. Let me give it a try.
Yeah, I like it！ Okay then...
(I got the "Latest Model of a Tennis Racket".)
Clerk
Um, can I have a word？ I'm actually looking for something.
Yes？
I'm looking for a pocket watch, like this one...
Ah, in that case, I have it.
What？ ...Can you give me that watch, please？
Let me think...
Instead... I'll give you this map.
...Okay, that's fine.
Thank you very much
(I got an "Old Map of Towano".)
Something interesting to see around here...
...A sticker, huh. Maybe I can use it for something.
(I got a "cute sheet of stickers".)
Fisherman
You come here often, nii-chan.
Me？ Well...
Do you like fish？ Then, I'll give you this.
What？ I mean, I don't mind it but are you sure...
No problem.
Then... Thank you.
No problem, see you.
(I got a "Fish Picture Book".)
Sailor
Hey, onii-san, you come here a lot.
Me？ Well...
Do you like boats？ Then I'll give you this.
What？ I'm okay with that, if you're sure you want to...
No problem. Take it.
Then... Thank you.
Well, see you around.
(I got a "Telescope".)
I've been here many times now... Let's see what's new.
...Huh？
Oh, this is...
(I got an "ammonite fossil".)
I've been to this store quite a bit...
I got a discount coupon... I'll come back soon.
(I got a discount coupon for the Restaurant by the Lake.)
I've been here many times, but I can't have a pet...
...Oh, stuffed animals are on sale.
I can't have pets, but I can have this one...
(I got a "Stuffed Dog".)
I'll see if I can find something that looks good...
Oh, a pillow... Looks really comfy to sleep in... Okay！
(I bought a "Pillow")
I wonder if I can find something to use...
Would it be useful to have a set of cookware...？
(I got a "Set of Fine Cookware".)
Let me see if there is interesting here...
...Huh, something fell down.
(I got the "Treasure Map".)
